      "description": "Offered is a collector-grade E46 M3 in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The Double-VANOS system has been meticulously serviced, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure structural rigidity. Finished with a functional limited-slip differential and a factory-spec suspension that retains original damping characteristics, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance. Mechanically flawless with documented preventative rod bearing replacement, it remains in showroom-quality state, ready for the most discerning purist.",
